💡 What I Learned

* A Bash script can be used to automate repetitive tasks.
* The output of one command can be sent directly to another command using a pipe (`|`).
* `nc` reads input from standard input, which makes it easy to test many inputs without typing them one by one.
* Even a simple brute-force attack can be automated with just a few lines of Bash.
